{"tid":28364,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"溫泉旅館","createTime":"2016-12-08T01:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T11:30:29.000Z","uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3e2fb4c53ec05138eca11bc4d80e4c9b41f9887","tid":28364,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:42:51.000Z","msg":"自從第一次住完日本溫泉旅館真係返唔到轉頭<br />\n大家有咩好推薦<br />\n<br />\n河口湖邊間係靚景，食物質素高，住得舒舒服服<br />\n<br />\n自己就睇啱湖山亭"},{"pid":"14bc23313e6a68a80d13e1e0e70bb49e7374b2b5","tid":28364,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:35:45.000Z","msg":"Lihk 0人流定冇人住溫泉旅館"},{"pid":"e4d044b9e72f6903a441ec32e62b1252732c6b80","tid":28364,"uid":48301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"留名，未浸過"},{"pid":"e8c82f9b59a42cd3c259c7d3a4112a4a093b8a38","tid":28364,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:44:19.000Z","msg":"住過三間:<br />\n別所溫泉 上松屋<br />\n島原溫泉 南風樓<br />\n祖谷溫泉 祖谷美人<br />\n上松屋中級溫泉旅館，性價比好，可以係房度食晚餐，同埋個溫泉啲味好似烚雞蛋幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n南風樓有露天私人風呂可以望海景浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祖谷美人有半露天私人風呂望山谷景，服務勁好，野食最好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984b4595b50abd4b50004beaeef19fa3cb25b640","tid":28364,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:52:24.000Z","msg":"浸過最舒服都係落住雪，一次晌新穗高一次晌藏王"},{"pid":"19280fdf359b3bca2914dac5a3cc4fa866f6053d","tid":28364,"uid":21871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:55:35.000Z","msg":"住過箱根aura橘<br />\n房入面有私人風呂幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過係山上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64025e8227840b93d09c8f32fb1f8518df631f2b","tid":28364,"uid":10035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>浸過最舒服都係落住雪，一次晌新穗高一次晌藏王</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第一次就係半露天係北海道落住雪浸<br />\n果種感覺真係爽撚到<br />\n個泉水好夠熱，硫磺味都幾勁，唔係加熱水"},{"pid":"817abf02f42f0655dfe04deda3609ccfe70ca517","tid":28364,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:03:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住過箱根aura橘<br />\n房入面有私人風呂幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過係山上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n九月份去左箱根吟遊，感覺夏天太熱，唔岩浸"},{"pid":"5d1fb4521b1c47cac3a684c5225b52890652c11e","tid":28364,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:12:19.000Z","msg":"反而 e + 唔知係咪老一輩女將退休, 少左果種賓至如歸既 feel <br />\n<br />\n老一輩果種貼心係非常難忘"},{"pid":"e90c8813329b600bba930fa75b70d405e6f34f27","tid":28364,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:14:33.000Z","msg":"價錢係幾多上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec0de46322fe05c94c8802092f468f4308d7292","tid":28364,"uid":5637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:16:50.000Z","msg":"搭單一問，鳥取三朝溫泉同皆生溫泉有咩好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228ec0b750270223f9ec66bab97adad1f862566a","tid":28364,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:02:31.000Z","msg":"將會住河口湖既千一景<br />\n大家係會揀私人風侶定係大浴池？"},{"pid":"dfccc9d5c9202a148939aeb42ac3e0aaaf2567c2","tid":28364,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"年頭 stay 過河口湖但冇住到溫泉旅館。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i238.photobucket.com/albums/ff47/ashleyroad/kawaguchiko%202016/DSCF0286.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi238.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fff47%2Fashleyroad%2Fkawaguchiko%25202016%2FDSCF0286.jpg&h=568642ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i238.photobucket.com/albums/ff47/ashleyroad/kawaguchiko%202016/DSCF0082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi238.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fff47%2Fashleyroad%2Fkawaguchiko%25202016%2FDSCF0082.jpg&h=d6399c28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i238.photobucket.com/albums/ff47/ashleyroad/kawaguchiko%202016/DSCF0128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi238.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fff47%2Fashleyroad%2Fkawaguchiko%25202016%2FDSCF0128.jpg&h=3d156140&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f58a23cdac7a5b20131c690be067f7bf50e693e","tid":28364,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自從第一次住完日本溫泉旅館真係返唔到轉頭<br />\n大家有咩好推薦<br />\n<br />\n河口湖邊間係靚景，食物質素高，住得舒舒服服<br />\n<br />\n自己就睇啱湖山亭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n河口湖o個頭可以考慮下別墅然然，雖然冇湖景但一樣睇到富士山。"},{"pid":"a7380455fb3a31ac35c2c63ce19b982494be3a50","tid":28364,"uid":60480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"book左greed lake似係民宿果類<br />\n有露天溫泉"},{"pid":"7f4727d8ee14b4f29afbb112c9ff55d269cc31f2","tid":28364,"uid":59666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"每次去日本都會特登揾幾間秘湯住"},{"pid":"1c8d71a7afb67732063d8ee9609d1e79a5fabf50","tid":28364,"uid":41359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}